---
layout: base.njk
title: Exonumist
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div>
      <h1>New York City Transportation Tokens</h1>
      <p>{{ site.notes.homepageTagline }}</p>
      <p class="note">Listed material on this site follows the {{ site.catalog.name }} where applicable.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/listed/" class="btn primary">Browse Listed Tokens</a>
        <a href="/unlisted/" class="btn">Explore Unlisted Tokens</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-visual-card">
        <img src="/images/official/630/630-d-a_o.jpg" alt="NY630Da obverse" />
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual-card">
        <img src="/images/official/630/630-d-a_r.jpg" alt="NY630Da reverse" />
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual-card">
        <strong>Collector-focused.</strong>
        <p class="note">Built around listed and unlisted New York City transportation-related tokens.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Listed Tokens</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">Browse listed New York City transportation-related tokens by borough and listed special groups.</p>
  <div class="grid-4">
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/628/"><article class="card"><strong>Bronx</strong><p>Listed Bronx transportation tokens.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/629/"><article class="card"><strong>Brooklyn</strong><p>Listed Brooklyn transportation tokens.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/630/"><article class="card"><strong>Manhattan</strong><p>Listed Manhattan transportation tokens.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/631/"><article class="card"><strong>Queens</strong><p>Listed Queens transportation tokens.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/632/"><article class="card"><strong>Staten Island</strong><p>Listed Staten Island transportation tokens.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/patterns/"><article class="card"><strong>Patterns</strong><p>Listed patterns from the {{ site.catalog.shortName }}.</p></article></a>
    <a class="card-link" href="/listed/club-tour/"><article class="card"><strong>Club Tour (CT)</strong><p>Listed club tour issues from the {{ site.catalog.shortName }}.</p></article></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Unlisted Tokens</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">
    New York City transportation-related tokens not presently included in the {{ site.catalog.name }}.
  </p>

  <div class="grid-3">
    <a class="card-link" href="/unlisted/">
      <article class="card">
        <strong>Unlisted Discoveries</strong>
        <p>
          Tokens and related material not presently listed in the
          {{ site.catalog.shortName }}.
        </p>
      </article>
    </a>

    <a class="card-link" href="/unlisted/#oddities">
      <article class="card">
        <strong>Oddities &amp; Errors</strong>
        <p>
          Unlisted errors, oddities, and unusual transportation-related material.
        </p>
      </article>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Resources</h2>
  <div class="grid-3">
    {% for resource in resources | sort(attribute="order") %}
      {% if resource.pub %}
      <a class="card-link" href="{{ resource.urlRef | resolveUrlRef(site) }}">
        <article class="resource-card">
          <strong>{{ resource.title }}</strong>
          <p>{{ resource.text }}</p>
        </article>
      </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>